MAMELODI Sundowns gifted its supporters with a strong 5-0 win over Amazulu in front of a home crowd on Sunday.But one very young Ka Bo Yellow  fan got a special chance to meet his idol from the Brazilans. Midfielder Themba ‘Mshishi’ Zwane took time from the team’s post match celebrations at Loftus Versfeld to meet the young boy standing by the sidelines. In a video posted on the PSL’s Twitter account, Mshishi hugs and picks up the boy who is excited to meet his hero.Soon after, the midfielder gifted took his t-shirt and gave it to his young fan.       